OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FITV News' Rob Smith reports from
OL,8,Foutside of Arrowe Park Hospital.
OL,10,FClinical assessments and testing are
OL,11,F"well under way" for passengers from
OL,12,Fthe cruise ship hit by deadly
OL,13,Fhantavirus, health bosses have said.
OL,15,FTwenty British nationals from the MV
OL,16,FHondius, together with a German who is
OL,17,Fa UK resident and a Japanese
OL,18,Fpassenger, were taken to Arrowe Park
OL,19,FHospital on the Wirral on Sunday after
OL,20,Fthe ship docked in Tenerife.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
