PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,8,Fsaid on Monday evening that clinical
OL,9,Fassessments and testing at the
OL,10,Fhospital were well under way.
OL,12,FArrowe Park will house the group for
OL,13,Fthree days in total before they are
OL,14,Fsent home to continue isolating for a
OL,15,Ffurther 42 days. If people cannot go
OL,16,Fhome, they will be placed in other
OL,17,Faccommodation to see out the isolation
OL,18,Fperiod.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,8,Fofficer at UKHSA, said: "Clinical
OL,9,Fassessments and testing are now under
OL,10,Fway at Arrowe Park and the staff there
OL,11,Fhave once again shown outstanding
OL,12,Fdedication and professionalism in
OL,13,Fproviding the highest standard of
OL,14,Fcare. We are enormously grateful for
OL,15,Feverything they are doing.
OL,17,F"Passengers will continue to receive
OL,18,Fthe full support of our teams and NHS
OL,19,Fspecialists throughout their stay and
OL,20,Fbeyond.
OL,26,@pD@YOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"We want to reassure both passengers
OL,8,Fand the wider public that robust
OL,9,Farrangements are in place, and that
OL,10,Feveryone involved will be looked after
OL,11,Fevery step of the way."
OL,13,FThe captain of the MV Hondius, Jan
OL,14,FDobrogowski, praised the crew and
OL,15,Fpassengers for the way they have
OL,16,Fmanaged on board.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
