OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FIn a video message, he said: "I've
OL,8,Fdecided to take this time to thank
OL,9,Fevery single guest and crew member on
OL,10,Fboard here, as well as our colleagues
OL,11,Fback home. The past few weeks have
OL,12,Fbeen extremely challenging to us all.
OL,14,F"What touched me the most, what moved
OL,15,Fme the most, was your patience, your
OL,16,Fdiscipline and also (the) kindness
OL,17,Fthat you showed to each other
OL,18,Fthroughout."
OL,26,@oD@^OUvD@AOUzD@LO]
