PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThree people have died linked to the
OL,8,Foutbreak. One British man with
OL,9,Fhantavirus is still being cared for in
OL,10,FJohannesburg and is thought to be
OL,11,Fimproving, while another is in the
OL,12,FNetherlands.
OL,14,FAnother British national has
OL,15,Fhantavirus and is isolating where he
OL,16,Flives on the remote South Atlantic
OL,17,FIsland of Tristan da Cunha.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
