PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778674272
OL,3,CHantavirus: Testing 'well under way'
OL,4,Cfor cruise Britons isolating at UK
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FOver the weekend, six paratroopers, an
OL,8,FRAF consultant, and an Army nurse from
OL,9,F16 Air Assault Brigade were parachuted
OL,10,Fon to Tristan da Cunha to help care
OL,11,Ffor him.
OL,13,FStrict infection control measures were
OL,14,Fin place throughout the journey to
OL,15,FArrowe Park, with passengers, crew,
OL,16,Fdrivers and medical teams all wearing
OL,17,Fpersonal protective equipment such as
OL,18,Fface masks.
OL,20,FThe UKHSA said strict measures remain
OL,21,Fin place at the hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
